            </rs> on the 1st. of this instant, the goods of <rs id="t16870114-39-viclabel191" type="occupation">Mr.</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-39-victim204 t16870114-39-viclabel191"></join> 
            
               
