                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-39-defend202 t16870114-39-deflabel192"></join> in his house, and had oftentimes robbed him before; so upon a full hearing, he was found <rs id="t16870114-39-verdict193" type="verdictDescription">
